Saved files format:
/scsi/www/backup_system/userid/files/FileName.d/date-Filename

Permissions:
/scsi/www/backup_system/data drwx------

Sample /etc/crontab entries:
# Remove deleted files from /usr/local/www/backup_system.
# Run command at 12 AM.
0	0	*	*	*	root	/usr/local/shell/bcksys_delete.sh

Only an administrator can clear a user's password. To do so, remove the file /path/to/backup_system/data/passwd.userid.
